'''彼得·勒文布雷·格里芬'''（'''Peter Löwenbräu<ref name="S02E01">{{cite episode|title=Peter, Peter, Caviar Eater|series=Family Guy|episodelink=Peter, Peter, Caviar Eater|serieslink=Family Guy|date=September 23, 1999|season=2|number=1}}</ref> Griffin'''）是美国喜剧动画《[[居家男人|居家男人]]》角色。由动画创始者[[塞思·麦克法兰|塞思·麦克法兰]]，第一次在1998年12月20日15分短片亮相。由麦克法兰亲自设计。格里芬一家出现在《[[Death_Has_a_Shadow|Death Has a Shadow]]》一集。

彼得和[[洛伊丝·格里芬|洛伊丝·格里芬]]结婚，是[[梅格·格里芬|梅格]]、[[克里斯·格里芬|克里斯]]和[[斯图威·格里芬|斯图伊]]的父亲。他也有一隻狗名为[[布赖恩·格里芬|布赖恩]]。他曾在一家玩具厂工作，现在在奎霍格啤酒公司。乍看之下只是[[郊區|郊區]]裡的[[藍領|藍領]]，其实他有些不凡的经验。

彼得的配音源自于麦克法兰他学校的看門人。麦克法兰取自以前动画短片《[[拉里的生活和拉里和史蒂夫|拉里的生活和拉里和史蒂夫]]》中主角拉里重新该角色设计。他曾出现在其他节目中，包括《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》、《[[南方公园|南方公园]]》、《[[卡通明星大亂鬥|卡通明星大亂鬥]]》、《[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]》和《[[克利夫兰秀|克利夫兰秀]]》。

== 在《居家男人》 ==
彼得·格里芬是[[爱尔兰裔美国人|爱尔兰裔美国人]]的工人阶级，体重[[过重|过重]]的[[蓝领|蓝领]]，带有[[罗得岛|罗得岛]]与东马萨诸塞州口音。<ref>{{cite news|title=Cavalcade Of Cartoons, No Joke: Animated Shows Make Up A Third Of The Midseason Replacements For Axed Fall Premieres|newspaper=[[The_Charlotte_Observer|The Charlotte Observer]]|date= January 10, 1999}}</ref>[[特尔玛·格里芬|特尔玛·格里芬]]与[[米基·麦克芬尼根|米基·麦克芬尼根]]的私生子，并当特尔玛和她的丈夫[[弗朗西斯·格里芬|弗朗西斯]]的儿子。彼得和他的家人住在罗得岛奎霍格。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Family Guy writer at Bryant|journal=The Providence Journal|date= September 24, 2008}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=''Family'' funny business|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|first=Michael|last=Hines|date=September 15, 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=James|first=Caryn|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9402E1DD1E39F93AA15752C0A96F958260|title=TV Weekend; Where Matricide Is a Family Value|publisher=New York Times|date=January 29, 1999|accessdate=November 23, 2008|archive-date=2008-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218205930/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9402E1DD1E39F93AA15752C0A96F958260}}</ref>彼得主要担任的Happy-Go-Lucky玩具厂安全督察，直到他的老板乔纳森·威德被小餐包窒息死亡；他后来成为一个渔夫在他自己的船，有两个[[葡萄牙人|葡萄牙人]]桑托斯和帕斯夸尔的帮助下入境，直到船被摧毁。<ref name=book>{{cite book|title=Family Guy: The Official Episode Guide, Seasons 1–3|url=https://archive.org/details/familyguyofficia00call|author=[[Steve_Callaghan|Callaghan, Steve]]|isbn=0-06-083305-X|chapter=A Hero Sits Next Door|page=[https://archive.org/details/familyguyofficia00call/page/32 32]|publisher=[[HarperCollins|HarperCollins]]|location=[[New_York_City|New York City]], [[New_York|New York]]|year=2005}}</ref><ref name=squad>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/09/18/family-guy-perfect-castaway/|publisher=[[TV_Squad|TV Squad]]|title=Perfect Castaway|accessdate=December 8, 2009|archive-date=2005-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051109203919/http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/09/18/family-guy-perfect-castaway/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他现在在波塔基特爱国者[[啤酒厂|啤酒厂]]（下港酒廠）航运部门。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.dvd.ign.com/articles/672/672389p1.html|title=Family Guy – Volume 3|date=November 29, 2005|accessdate=September 10, 2009|last=Drucker|first=Mike|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-date=2008-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081225005704/http://uk.dvd.ign.com/articles/672/672389p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.popmatters.com/tv/reviews/f/family-guy-2005.shtml|date=June 13, 2005|title=Family Guy / American Dad|publisher=[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]|author=Wong, Kevin|accessdate=July 4, 2009|archive-date=2008-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509105418/http://www.popmatters.com/tv/reviews/f/family-guy-2005.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 关于人物 ==

=== 创作 ===
麦克法兰在1995年[[罗德岛設計学院|罗德岛設計学院]]（RISD）学习动画时最初构想《居家男人》。<ref name="Lenburg">{{cite book|last=Lenburg|first=Jeff|title=Who's Who in Animated Cartoons: An International Guide to Film & Television's Award-Winning and Legendary Animators|url=https://archive.org/details/whoswhoinanimate0000lenb|publisher=Applause Theatre & Cinema Books|location=New York|year=2006|edition=Illustrated|page=[https://archive.org/details/whoswhoinanimate0000lenb/page/221 221]|isbn=978-1-55783-671-7}}</ref>大学期间，他创作专题电影题为《[[拉里的生活和拉里和史蒂夫|拉里的生活]]》，<ref name="Lenburg"/>而他作品由教授直交至[[汉纳巴伯拉动画|汉纳巴伯拉动画]]，因此麦克法兰被公司受雇。<ref name="harvard">{{cite news|last=Lenburg|first=Jeff|title="Family Guy" Seth MacFarlane to speak at Class Day: Creator and executive producer of 'Family Guy' will headline undergraduate celebration|url=http://www.news.harvard.edu/gazette/2006/05.11/03-classday.html|work=[[Harvard_Gazette|Harvard Gazette]]|accessdate=December 21, 2007|date=May 11, 2006|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69hkeIvCX?url=http://www.news.harvard.edu/gazette/2006/05.11/03-classday.html|archive-date=2012-08-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在1996年麦克法兰创作拉里的生活续集《[[拉里的生活和拉里和史蒂夫|拉里和史蒂夫]]》，就是一个中年角色名为拉里和有智能的狗史蒂夫；在1997年该短片播出于[[卡通頻道|卡通頻道]]的《妙妙卡通秀》。<ref name="Lenburg"/>[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯]]高主管看到《拉里》短片就包麦克法兰创作以此短片改编成《居家男人》的角色。<ref name="Bartlett">{{cite web|url = http://greatreporter.com/mambo/content/view/1383/11/|title = Seth MacFarlane – he’s the "Family Guy"|accessdate = December 31, 2007|last = Bartlett|first = James|date = March 12, 2007|work = The Great Reporter|publisher = Presswire Limited|archive-date = 2012-01-21|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/64qmhYUhM?url=http://greatreporter.com/content/seth-macfarlane-he-s-family-guy|dead-url = no}}</ref>福克斯提出麦克法兰完成一部15分钟长的短片，并给了他五万美元预算。<ref name="megadeal">{{cite news|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|title="Family Guy" creator seals megadeal|date=May 5, 2008|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSN0435504220080505|accessdate=May 31, 2008|archive-date=2012-08-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69hkgX9Bh?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/05/us-macfarlane-idUSN0435504220080505|dead-url=no}}</ref>《居家男人》的几个要点是由《拉里》短片而来的。<ref name="Callaghan, p. 16">[[#Callaghan|Callaghan]], p. 16</ref>拉里和他的狗史蒂夫渐渐变成彼得和布赖恩。<ref name="Bartlett"/><ref name="AWN">{{cite news|url=http://www.awn.com/news/events/cartoon-network-pilots-screened-asifa-east-nycs-school-visual-arts|title=Cartoon Network Pilots Screened by ASIFA East at NYC's School of Visual Arts|author=Strike, Joe|publisher=[[Animation_World_Network|Animation World Network]]|accessdate=November 18, 2009|archive-date=2012-08-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69hkhPSY9?url=http://www.awn.com/news/events/cartoon-network-pilots-screened-asifa-east-nycs-school-visual-arts|dead-url=no}}</ref>麦克法兰表示，《拉里的生活》和《居家男人》的不同为，《拉里的生活》主要是在宿舍裡展示亮相，《居家男人》在[[第三十三届超级碗|第三十三届超级碗]]後亮相<ref name="Callaghan, p. 16"/>。

=== 配音 ===
彼得的配音是由麦克法兰所配，也是布赖恩、斯图伊和奎麦尔的配音，麦克法兰也最突出提供了声音，其他各种经常性和一次性的特点，[[汤姆·塔克_(居家男人)|汤姆·塔克]], [[卡特·皮尤特施密特|卡特·皮尤特施密特]]和哈特曼医生<ref>{{cite news|title=Cartoonist MacFarlane funny guy of Fox's 'Family' Subversive voice of series is his|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|author=Graham, Jefferson|date=January 29, 1999|page=E7}}</ref>。麦克法兰从一开始至今已经是這動画的主要配音员。<ref name="TVGuide cast"/>麦克法兰选择彼得的声音，其余部分角色也由他配，认为这样比让别人来做更容易。<ref name="MacFarlaneTIME">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1844711,00.html|title=Family Guy's Seth MacFarlane|author=Cruz, Gilbert|date=September 26, 2008|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|accessdate=August 28, 2009|archive-date=2012-08-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69hpKmP3m?url=http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1844711,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>麦克法兰的音色不像彼得的配音，他用正常声音在布赖恩。<ref name="MacFarlaneTIME"/>在出席[[罗德岛設計学院|罗德岛設計学院]]时，麦克法兰的灵感从一名他偷听谈话保安而得到彼得的声音；<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.projo.com/tv/content/projo_20050430_macfarlan.1d6c9b8.html|work=Prohaving the vidence Journal TV|author=Smith, Andy|title=A Real Family Reunion|date=April 30, 2005|accessdate=August 28, 2009|archive-date=2010-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922180650/http://www.projo.com/tv/content/projo_20050430_macfarlan.1d6c9b8.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>麦克法兰配彼得的祖先都是同一类的配音。<ref name="TVGuide cast">{{cite web |url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/family-guy/cast/100148 |title=Family Guy Cast and Details |work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]] |accessdate=August 24, 2009 |archive-date=2012-08-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69hpZKLsJ?url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/family-guy/cast/100148 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在採访上指出他配彼得及其余部分角色，另一方面是因为他们最初有一些小预算且更有弹性。<ref name=avclub>{{cite web |url=http://www.avclub.com/content/node/23365 |title=Seth MacFarlane |accessdate=September 26, 2007 |last=Rabin |first=Nathan |date=January 26, 2006 |work=The A.V. Club |publisher=Onion, Inc. |archive-date=2008-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081221125220/http://www.avclub.com/content/node/23365 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在另一次采访中，他提到彼得的声音是最难配的。<ref name="Road to">{{cite web|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/429/429628p10.html|title=Interview with Seth MacFarlane|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=December 9, 2009|archive-date=2012-02-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65Ak8AEDh?url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/429/429628p10.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
麦克法兰在几个场景没有配彼得。除了在“No Meals on Wheels”一集中是由[[帕特里克·斯图尔特|帕特里克·斯图尔特]]所配，其余集数都是麦克法兰的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmovie.com/cg/avg.dll?p=avg&sql=2:68265~T2 |title=Patrick Stewart > Filmography |accessdate=February 27, 2009 |publisher=[[Allmovie|Allmovie]] |archive-date=2012-04-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66qsaynlq?url=http://www.allmovie.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在“[[Family_Gay|Family Gay]]”一集中[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]客串配彼得的配音。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/episode/200320/castcrew|title=Family Guy — Family Gay — Cast and Crew|publisher=Yahoo!|accessdate=July 21, 2011|archive-date=2012-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101141130/http://tv.yahoo.com/episode/200320/castcrew}}</ref>在“[[Road_to_the_Multiverse|Road to the Multiverse]]”一集中全世界都是日本人的场景由日本演员詹姆森·杨所配。<ref name="cast">{{cite web |url=http://tv.yahoo.com/episode/217820/castcrew |title=Family Guy – Road to the Multiverse – Cast and Crew |publisher=Yahoo! |accessdate=April 4, 2010 |archive-date=2012-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031130813/http://tv.yahoo.com/episode/217820/castcrew |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 人格 ===
蓝领彼得<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/family-guy-3-dvd/#|title=Family Guy, Volume 3|work=[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]|date=November 29, 2005|author=MacIntosh, Dan|accessdate=October 18, 2009|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103115523/http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/family-guy-3-dvd}}</ref>经常与他的邻居[[克利夫兰·布朗|克利夫兰]]、[[乔·斯旺森|乔]]和[[格伦·奎麦尔|奎麦尔]]在酒吧“醉蛤（The Drunken Clam）”，喝得醉薰薰。<ref>{{cite news|title='Family Guy Live' a fresh channel for laughs|author=McNarma, Chris|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=September 14, 2007|page=1}}</ref>做完[[智商|智商测验]]后，彼得发现他智力下降略低于[[智障|智障]]。<ref name="Petarded">{{cite episode|title=Petarded|episodelink=Petarded|series=Family Guy|credits=Writ.: Sulkin, Alec; Wild, Wellesley; Dir.: Kearsley, Seth|network=[[Fox_Broadcasting_Company|Fox Broadcasting Company]]|airdate= June 19, 2005|season=4|number=6}}</ref>彼得性情急躁易冲动时发生一些难堪情况下，<ref>{{cite news|title=Union guy is 'Family Guy'|url=http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=8129157|author=Nearing, Brian|date=May 31, 2009|work=[[Albany_Times_Union|Albany Times Union]]|accessdate=October 18, 2009|page=C1|archive-date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140805125133/http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=8129157|dead-url=no}}</ref>如对[[调戏|调戏]]梅格用[[redneck|乡巴佬]]生活方式。<ref>{{cite episode|title=Airport '07|episodelink=Airport '07|series=Family Guy|credits=Writ.: Devanney, Tom; Hentemann, Mark; Dir.: Holmquist, John|network=[[Fox_Broadcasting_Company|Fox Broadcasting Company]]|airdate= March 4, 2007|season=5|number=12}}</ref> 他嫉妒等景点洛伊丝在她的生活，这导致了极端情况下的态度，比如在[[海洋世界|海洋世界]]他袭击吻洛伊丝的鲸鱼。<ref name="glue"/>在[[居家男人_(第三季)|第三季]]“[[Stuck_Together,_Torn_Apart|Stuck Together, Torn Apart]]”一集，因为彼得的嫉妒而和洛伊丝分裂，卻意外发现洛伊丝具有相同的嫉妒的本质才住在一起。<ref name="glue">{{cite episode|title=Stuck Together, Torn Apart|episodelink=Stuck Together, Torn Apart|series=Family Guy|credits=Writ.: Hentemann, Mark; Dir.: DiMartino, Michael Dante|network=[[Fox_Broadcasting_Company|Fox Broadcasting Company]]|airdate=2002-01-31|season=3|number=19}}</ref>彼得有短暂注意力导致他怪异的情况下，“[[Long_John_Peter|Long John Peter]]”中克里斯指出彼得的鹦鹉死亡后才想起一件事，然后到另一地方，彼得找到[[管风琴|管风琴]]但忘记他的鹦鹉（彼得然后在几秒内破坏管风琴，然后找到一张养牛场的契约）。<ref>{{cite episode|title=Long John Peter|episodelink=Long John Peter|series=Family Guy|credits=Writ.: Devanney, Tom; Hentemann, Mark; Dir.: Holmquist, John|network=[[Fox_Broadcasting_Company|Fox Broadcasting Company]]|airdate= March 4, 2007|season=6|number=12}}</ref>

