20809024603/http://tv.ign.com/articles/100/1005692p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 彼得排名在第三位的IGN所列出的“前25名《居家男人》角色”名单，在列表中显示许多节目最佳噱头来自彼得，有人认定彼得实际上发明“海牛笑话”。<ref name=matee>{{cite web|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=|author=Haque, Ahsan|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/987/987014p8.html|title=Top 25 Family Guy Characters|accessdate=July 22, 2011|archive-date=2011-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111129040349/http://tv.ign.com/articles/987/987014p8.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>彼得列也在《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的“前十八名电视坏爸爸”名单中。<ref>{{cite web|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=June 7, 2011|author=EW Staff|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20502369,00.html#20976609|title=18 Bad TV Dads — Peter Griffin|accessdate=July 22, 2011|archive-date=2014-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140901055331/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20502369,00.html#20976609}}</ref>

=== 批评和争议 ===
彼得曾被批评像[[霍默·辛普森|霍默·辛普森]]。彼得出现在《辛普森一家》的一些集数里，被形容是辛普森的克隆版或[[抄袭|抄袭]]。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的肯·塔克说，彼得是霍默·辛普森的原案，没有参考其他电视节目。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,273010,00.html|title=Family Guy|last=Tucker|first=Ken|date=June 9, 1999|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=June 19, 2011|archive-date=2012-08-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69zPffQ8D?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,273010,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《电视评论家》的罗宾·皮尔逊批评《恶搞之家》太像《辛普森一家》。<ref name="TV Critic">{{cite web|url=http://thetvcritic.org/death-has-a-shadow/|title=Episode 1: Death Has a Shadow|last=Pierson|first=Robin|work=The TV Critic|accessdate=June 19, 2011|date=August 7, 2009|archive-date=2012-08-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69zPeS0FY?url=http://thetvcritic.org/reviews/comedies/family-guy/season-39/death-has-a-shadow/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最终在《[[Ratings_Guy|Ratings Guy]]》一集显示一件趣事，彼得毁了电视，到电视台改変节目，随之而来的是霍默·辛普森表达同样的困境，彼得说“哈！看来你们也抄袭我们！（A-ha! Looks like this is one WE beat YOU to!）”<ref>{{cite episode| title = Ratings Guy | credits=Writ.:Ihlenfeld, Dave & Wright, David ; Dir.: Purdum, James | episodelink = Ratings Guy | airdate= October 7, 2012| season = 11| number = 2| series = Family Guy| network=FOX}}</ref>

彼得在《居家男人》的各集引起争议。在《[[The_Cleveland-Loretta_Quagmire|The Cleveland-Loretta Quagmire]]》的歌名《你有艾滋病》，当中彼得·格里芬用四重唱的方式围绕一个关于因[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]臨终的男人，这引来几个艾滋病服务组织的抗议。<ref name="fgaids">{{cite web| url = http://www.advocate.com/exclusive_detail_ektid19925.asp| title = "Family Guy" has fun with AIDS| author = Adams, Bob| work = Advocate.com| publisher = PlanetOut Inc.| accessdate = December 12, 2006| date = August 22, 2005| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050923175341/http://advocate.com/exclusive_detail_ektid19925.asp| archivedate = 2005年9月23日| quote = ... showcases a comic musical number called “You Have AIDS.” Overburdened AIDS service organizations are not amused.| deadurl = yes}}</ref> 在《[[When_You_Wish_Upon_a_Weinstein|When You Wish Upon a Weinstein]]》，彼得唱《我需要犹太》是恶搞自[[Leigh_Harline|Leigh Harline]]所唱的《[[当你向星星许愿|当你向星星许愿]]》的歌曲；2007年10月3日，[[伯恩有限公司音乐出版商|伯恩有限公司音乐出版商]]提起诉讼，指控侵犯原曲版权的节目；伯恩有限公司，是唯一这首歌的美国版权拥有者，指控恶搞原曲副本对比他们[[反犹太主义|反犹太主义]]的歌词。<ref>{{cite court|litigants=Bourne Co., vs. Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Fox Broadcasting Company, Twentieth Century Fox Television, Inc., Twentieth Century Fox Home Entertainment, Inc., Fuzzy Door Productions, Inc., The Cartoon Network, Inc., Seth MacFarlane, Walter Murphy |court=[[United_States_District_Court_for_the_Southern_District_of_New_York|United States District Court, Southern District of New York]] |date=October 3, 2007|accessdate=September 5, 2010|url=http://www.schwimmerlegal.com/family%20guy%20complaint.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>该投诉并没有维持原判。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSTRE52F6W620090316?feedType=RSS| title="Family Guy" Wins Court Battle Over song| accessdate=March 17, 2009| publisher=reuters.com| first=Christine| last=Kearney| date=March 16, 2009| archive-date=2012-01-21| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64qmi6sb8?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/16/us-usa-familyguy-song-idUSTRE52F6W620090316?feedType=RSS| dead-url=no}}</ref>

