彼得已经出现在《辛普森一家》两集，这​​两个节目经常互相比较。在[[辛普森一家_(第十四季)|第十四季]]《[[恐怖的树屋XIII|恐怖的树屋XIII]]》，彼得为[[霍默·辛普森|霍默·辛普森]]的克隆，<ref>{{cite news|title=Family Guy and The Simpsons|author=Finley, Adam|publisher=[[TV_Squad|TV Squad]]|url=http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/07/14/family-guy-and-the-simpsons/|date=July 14, 2005|accessdate=October 19, 2009|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226192648/http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/07/14/family-guy-and-the-simpsons/}}</ref> 而在[[辛普森一家（第十七季）|第十七季]]《[[The_Italian_Bob|The Italian Bob]]》，彼得的照片是一本书中的罪犯，通缉名“plagiarismo”（意大利文，意指抄袭）。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Simpsons: The Italian Bob|author=Budke, Ryan|publisher=[[TV_Squad|TV Squad]]|url=http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/12/12/the-simpsons-the-italian-bob/|date=December 12, 2005|accessdate=October 19, 2009|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226190953/http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/12/12/the-simpsons-the-italian-bob/}}</ref>彼得也出现在《[[克利夫兰秀|克利夫兰秀]]》。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.medialifemagazine.com/artman2/publish/TV_Reviews_21/Cleveland_Show_acquired_lack_of_taste.asp|title=Cleveland Show, acquired lack of taste|author=Conroy, Tom|work=Media Life Magazine|date=October 8, 2009|accessdate=October 19, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091014223117/http://www.medialifemagazine.com/artman2/publish/TV_Reviews_21/Cleveland_Show_acquired_lack_of_taste.asp|archivedate=2009年10月14日}}</ref>此外，彼得还出现《[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]》《[[飓风!_(特工老爹)|飓风！]]》的片尾，與[[斯坦·史密斯_(特工老爹)|斯坦·史密斯]]、曾搬出去又搬回來的的邻居[[克利夫兰·布朗|克利夫兰·布朗（台譯達叔）]]展开枪战。斯坦打中弗朗辛，彼得就说这是“经典特工老爹！”。

