列入其他《居家男人》週边商品。<ref>{{cite news|title='Family Guy' after brand world domination|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1000902881#|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|author=Wallenstein, Andrew|date=April 29, 2005|accessdate=October 19, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071007044033/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1000902881|archive-date=2007-10-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

